Proc read and write module linux kernel 4.15

Installing the linux headers

You need to install the linux-headers-.. first as shown below. Depending on your distro, use apt-get or yum.

# apt-get install build-essential linux-headers-$(uname -r)

Next, create the following proc.c module in C programming language.

reate Makefile to Compile Kernel Module

The following makefile can be used to compile the above basic proc read and write module linux kernel

Use the make command to compile proc read and write module linux kernel as shown below.
